{"tid":96603,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)大英雄聯盟  LEGO英雄傳 街霸2","createTime":"2017-01-27T03:28:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-27T08:03:59.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"557a4c23b63852d7f7bfa56bfdf825a0ffd332e1","tid":96603,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T03:28:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=GQs%2F0oZ20mHpatel3Nm0o2N6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=e17587c1\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> 關左ADBLOCK可以睇到V台好似係 按左下可轉CC台<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=GQs%2F0oZ20mHpatel3Nm0o2N6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=774aca58\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a>可以直接睇到V台<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/4/4b/Big_Hero_6_%28film%29_poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F4%2F4b%2FBig_Hero_6_%2528film%2529_poster.jpg&h=2b8dc9cf&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/1/10/The_Lego_Movie_poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F1%2F10%2FThe_Lego_Movie_poster.jpg&h=3efbcb27&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://i68.tinypic.com/2j5nae8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi68.tinypic.com%2F2j5nae8.jpg&h=8118147f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.14歲發明天才少年濱田廣（Hiro Hamada）最新發明「微型機器人」，竟然令他捲入足以摧毀舊京山的巨大陰謀！孤立無援，阿廣只能藉助一班另類勢力，由宅宅實驗室裡四個哥哥的朋友包括芥末無薑(Wasabi-No-Ginger)、化學天才哈妮蕾夢（Honey Lemon）、單車信差神行蛋葆（Go Go Tomago）、宅男漫畫迷費吉拉（Fred）及醫護機器人杯麵（Baymax）。阿廣為朋友和自己配上了高科技超級裝備，6人組成了能力非凡的「大英雄天團」<br />\n<br />\n2.故事設定於樂高宇宙，所有的人物和建築物都是樂高組成的。故事一開始，維特長老試圖保護一種超級武器「瘋膠魔」（強力膠）以免落入邪惡的企業總裁手中，但企業總裁帶領著部下現身將瘋膠魔奪走，並弄瞎了維特長老的雙眼，得意的總裁正打算離身而去時，長老預言將會有個「非凡」的人會成為救世主來阻止瘋膠魔，說完便被總裁踹到山谷下..<br />\n<br />\n3.1994年公映。維加擁有邪惡的力量，能用意念控制人。他組建了沙杜盧組織，在世界各地派出監視人造人，以尋求格鬥術高強的街頭戰士，然後用意念控制他們，使其成爲自己的殺人工具。國際刑警春麗和美軍空軍古列少佐，聯手調查此組織。維加派出三大殺手加以阻撓，他們是沙加特（泰拳王，在泰國受到英雄般的崇拜，但幾年前敗在流浪格鬥家龍的手上）、拜森（重量級拳王，因過于殘忍而被拳壇除名）、巴洛克（毒蛇般的西班牙殺手）。龍的好友也是他師弟的格鬥家肯不幸被維加用意念控制。龍爲了消滅維加以及救出肯，和正義的格鬥家們向邪惡勢力發出挑戰...<br />\n<br />\n12 00PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88e044ff6f93c0b3da1054e855e5b954994768c7","tid":96603,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T03:34:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e6f645d48696ae677110621f15958e0e4da83b5","tid":96603,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T04:16:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cd58e092bffb1c487d2de49a9079bb19ace5961","tid":96603,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T05:02:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffeae299a1a1ec43ca664c69bce85e175c51e26f","tid":96603,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T05:25:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5ffed47b048f27d47f804e9926cfff46047166a","tid":96603,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T06:08:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gi